'''柯瑞·德魯·席格'''（{{lang-en|'''Corey Drew Seager'''}}，{{bd|1994年|4月27日}}），為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[游擊手|游擊手]]，目前效力於德州遊騎兵。他先前曾效力於洛杉磯道奇。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
席格出生於[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡]][[夏洛特_(北卡羅來納州)|夏洛特]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/la-sp-seager-hr-derby-plaschke-20160707-snap-story.html|title=For the Dodgers, Corey Seager in the home run derby could be a disaster|first=Bill|last=Plaschke|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-11|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095521/https://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/la-sp-seager-hr-derby-plaschke-20160707-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高中時期就讀於[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡]][[坎納波利斯|坎納波利斯]]的Northwest Cabarrus High School{{譯名請求}}，席格原先預計在畢業後進入[[南卡羅來納大學|南卡大學]]，後來與[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]簽約（2012年首輪第18順位，簽約金2,350,000美元），進入職棒系統。
{{expand section}}

== 職棒生涯 ==
席格在2013年被升至高階1A，由於成績有所落差，他在季後前往{{le|亞利桑那秋季聯盟|Arizona Fall League}}，持續棒球活動。2014年，席格被選入[[美國大聯盟未來之星明星賽|未來之星明星賽]]<ref name=gurnick062414>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140624&content_id=81368148&notebook_id=81398432&vkey=notebook_la&c_id=la |title=Seager, Urias named to Futures Game roster |first=Ken |last=Gurnick |work=MLB.com |date=2014-06-24 |accessdate=2014-06-24 |archive-date=2014-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718102147/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140624&content_id=81368148&notebook_id=81398432&vkey=notebook_la&c_id=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後提升至小聯盟2A<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/dodgersnow/la-sp-dn-dodgers-promote-corey-seager-20140713-story.html |title=Dodgers promote top prospect Corey Seager to double-A Chattanooga |work=The Los Angeles Times |first=Bill |last=Shaikin |date=2014-07-13 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019212214/http://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/dodgersnow/la-sp-dn-dodgers-promote-corey-seager-20140713-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他持續高檔表現，38場出賽中有.345打擊率的成績。並入選《Baseball America》{{譯名請求}}的小聯盟明星隊名單<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-star-team-2014/|title = Minor League All-Star Team 2014|first = Matt|last = Eddy|work = ''Baseball America''|date = 2014-09-03|accessdate = 2015-09-19|archive-date = 2017-11-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171107011106/http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-star-team-2014/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，他與[[賈克·彼得森|賈克·彼得森]]同為道奇系統的年度小聯盟球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.truebluela.com/2014/9/26/6851871/joc-pederson-julio-urias-corey-seager-dodgers-minor-league-awards|title=Joc Pederson, Corey Seager, Julio Urias named Dodgers minor league players of the year|first=Eric|last=Stephen|work=truebluela.com|date=2014-09-26|accessdate=2014-09-26|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414112109/https://www.truebluela.com/2014/9/26/6851871/joc-pederson-julio-urias-corey-seager-dodgers-minor-league-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年季初，席格受邀大聯盟春訓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dodgers.mlblogs.com/2015/01/09/arruebarrena-seager-urias-among-17-non-roster-spring-training-invitees/|title=Arruebarrena, Seager, Urias among 17 non-roster Spring Training invitees|work=dodgers.com|first=Jon|last=Weisman|date=2015-01-09|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2016-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605113607/http://dodgers.mlblogs.com/2015/01/09/arruebarrena-seager-urias-among-17-non-roster-spring-training-invitees/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大聯盟官方網站評價席格為排名第7的新秀球員，《Baseball America》則評為百大新秀第5<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/2015-top-100-prospects/t/arizona-diamondbacks/|title=2015 Top 100 Prospects|work=Baseball America|date=2015-02-20|access-date=2020-10-03|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911073100/http://www.baseballamerica.com/2015-top-100-prospects/t/arizona-diamondbacks/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.truebluela.com/2015/1/30/7954849/dodgers-prospects-mlb|title = Dodgers have 3 prospects in MLB.com top 13|work = True Blue LA|date = 2015-01-30|last = Stephen|first = Eric|access-date = 2020-10-03|archive-date = 2020-11-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128193350/https://www.truebluela.com/2015/1/30/7954849/dodgers-prospects-mlb|dead-url = no}}</ref>。開季後，席格自2A起步，20場的出賽便有.375的打擊率，使他在5月1日被升至3A<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/seager-660177-dodgers-prospect.html|title=Dodgers promote blue-chip prospect Corey Seager to Triple-A|work=Orange County Register|first=Bill|last=Plunkett|date=2015-04-30|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306090720/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/seager-660177-dodgers-prospect.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月28日的比賽，席格單場6次擊出安打<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150528&content_id=127197546&fext=.jsp&vkey=recap&sid=t238|title=Seager Dazzles in Salt Lake with Six Hits, Six RBI|work=milb.com|date=2015-05-28|accessdate=2015-05-28|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706081421/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150528&content_id=127197546&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&sid=t238|dead-url=no}}</ref>。季末再次入選《Baseball America》小聯盟明星隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-star-team-2015/|title=Minor League All-Star Team 2015|first=Matt|last=Eddy|work=Baseball America|date=2015-09-09|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2017-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531110215/http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-star-team-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時亦是3A的年度球員<ref name=ba091115>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/2015-classification-star-teams/|title=2015 Minor League Classification All-Star Teams|work=Baseball America|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-11|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706145538/http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/2015-classification-star-teams/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===洛杉磯道奇===
====2015年球季====
2015年9月3日，道奇將席格升上大聯盟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsok.com/report-dodgers-to-promote-top-prospect-corey-seager/article/5444291|title=Report: Dodgers to promote top prospect Corey Seager|first=Jacob|last=Unruh|work=NewOK|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2015-09-03|archive-date=2017-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602184303/http://newsok.com/report-dodgers-to-promote-top-prospect-corey-seager/article/5444291|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當天他有2支安打的表現，首安更是右外野方向的二壘安打<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2015_09_03_lanmlb_sdnmlb_1&lang=en#game=2015_09_03_lanmlb_sdnmlb_1,game_state=Wrapup,game_tab=play-by-play |title=Padres 10, Dodgers 7 play-by-play |work=mlb.com |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090743/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2015_09_03_lanmlb_sdnmlb_1&lang=en#game=2015_09_03_lanmlb_sdnmlb_1,game_state=Wrapup,game_tab=play-by-play |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月12日，在對陣[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]的賽事中，四次打擊全部擊出安打，包括他的大聯盟首轟。9月21日，席格連續16場比賽上壘，打破了道奇隊史的新秀紀錄{{efn|原紀錄持有人為Bill Russell{{譯名請求}}。}}<ref name=stephen092115>{{cite web |url=http://www.truebluela.com/2015/9/21/9369145/dodgers-diamondbacks-recap-extra-base-hits |title=Diamondbacks do extra to finally beat Dodgers in LA |work=SB Nation |first=Eric |last=Stephen |date=2015-09-21 |accessdate=2015-09-22 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020220511/https://www.truebluela.com/2015/9/21/9369145/dodgers-diamondbacks-recap-extra-base-hits |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季末結算，席格的成績極為傑出（打擊率.337，全壘打4，打點17<ref name=br>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/seageco01.shtml|title=Corey Seager Statistics & History|work=Baseball Reference|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330172018/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/seageco01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>），道奇在[[2015年国家联盟分区赛|國聯分區系列賽]]中啟用他為先發游擊手，使席格成為道奇隊史最年輕的季後賽先發野手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20151009/corey-seager-is-youngest-la-dodgers-position-player-to-start-in-postseason|title=Corey Seager is youngest LA Dodgers position player to start in postseason|work=Los Angeles Daily News|first=J.P.|last=Hoornstra|date=2015-10-09|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2016-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115195943/http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20151009/corey-seager-is-youngest-la-dodgers-position-player-to-start-in-postseason|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====2016年球季====
席格在2016年球季的開幕戰中擔任先發游擊手，是1944年以來的隊史最年輕紀錄{{efn|原紀錄持有人為Gene Mauch{{譯名請求}}。}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.truebluela.com/2016/4/4/11310078/corey-seager-opening-day-lineup-dodgers-padres |title=Corey Seager is youngest opening day Dodgers SS in 72 years |work=SB Nation |first=Eric |last=Stephen |date=2016-04-04 |accessdate=2016-04-05 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024111020/https://www.truebluela.com/2016/4/4/11310078/corey-seager-opening-day-lineup-dodgers-padres |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月3日，單場三次擊出全壘打，被選為6月的最佳新秀<ref name=baer070216>{{cite web |url=http://m.dodgers.mlb.com/news/article/187526626/corey-seager-named-nls-top-rookie-for-june |title=Seager named NL's top rookie for June |first=Jack |last=Baer |work=dodgers.com |date=2016-07-02 |accessdate=2016-07-02 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008154147/http://m.dodgers.mlb.com/news/article/187526626/corey-seager-named-nls-top-rookie-for-june/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並入選國聯明星隊<ref name=weisman070516>{{cite web |url=http://dodgers.mlblogs.com/2016/07/05/jansen-kershaw-seager-named-to-nl-all-star-team/ |title=Jansen, Kershaw, Seager named to NL All-Star team |work=Dodgers.com |first=Jon |last=Weisman |date=2016-07-05 |accessdate=July 5, 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708082925/http://dodgers.mlblogs.com/2016/07/05/jansen-kershaw-seager-named-to-nl-all-star-team/ |archivedate=2016-07-08 }}</ref>。他參與了全明星週的全壘打大賽，在第一輪擊出15支全壘打，未能晉級，但其成績已是道奇隊史次佳<ref name=walton0711116>{{cite web |url=http://www.truebluela.com/2016/7/11/12155988/corey-seager-was-great-no-match-for-mark-trumbo-in-home-run-derby |title=Corey Seager was great, no match for Mark Trumbo in Home Run Derby |work=SB Nation |first=Ryan |last=Walton |date=July 11, 2016 |accessdate=July 11, 2016 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024162326/https://www.truebluela.com/2016/7/11/12155988/corey-seager-was-great-no-match-for-mark-trumbo-in-home-run-derby |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

8月6日，席格擊出賽季的第31支二壘安打，打破了道奇隊史的新秀紀錄{{efn|原紀錄持有人為Eric Karros{{譯名請求}}。}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/194017390/ross-stripling-dodgers-shut-out-red-sox/?game_pk=448505 |title=Stripling steps up, Dodgers shut out Red Sox |first1=Jack |last1=Baer |last2=Roberts |first2=Quinn |work=MLB.com |date=2016-08-06 |accessdate=2016-08-07 |archive-date=2016-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815150743/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/194017390/ross-stripling-dodgers-shut-out-red-sox/?game_pk=448505 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月27日，在比賽第一局面對[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]的Jason Hammel{{譯名請求}}擊出全壘打，這不只是本季個人的第23支全壘打，也因此打破了高懸86年游擊手單季最多轟的隊史紀錄{{efn|原紀錄持有人為Glenn Wright{{譯名請求}}（1930年）。}}<ref>[http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/08/28/2219725 席格打破高懸86年的道奇隊史紀錄] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/08/28/2219725 |date=20170304193808 }}，[[今日新聞網|今日新聞網]]，2016-08-28</ref>。9月17日，突破了道奇隊史的新秀年安打紀錄{{efn|原紀錄持有人為Steve Sax{{譯名請求}}（1982年）。}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/201906114/dodgers-beat-d-backs-on-joc-pederson-homer/?game_pk=449079|title=Pederson powers Dodgers closer to postseason|first=Ken and Jake Rill|last=Gurnick|work=mlb.com|date=2016-09-18|accessdate=2016-09-19|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919225727/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/201906114/dodgers-beat-d-backs-on-joc-pederson-homer/?game_pk=449079|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月20日，擊出賽季第40支二壘安打。季末，席格獲得[[美國職棒大聯盟年度最佳新人獎|國聯最佳新人獎]]殊榮<ref>[https://tsna.com/article/8255 國聯新人王加身　Seager：還不滿足]，[[TSNA|TSNA]]，2017-02-23</ref>，並被《Baseball America》等多家媒體選為年度最佳新秀<ref name=glaser100516>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/corey-seager-proves-can-star-shortstop/#hsQJ8HmCzBKeVrby.97 |title=Corey Seager proves he can be a star at shortstop |first=Kyle |last=Glaser |work=Baseball America |date=2016-10-05 |accessdate=2016-10-14 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220012707/https://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/corey-seager-proves-can-star-shortstop/#hsQJ8HmCzBKeVrby.97 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=fagan102416>{{cite web |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/news/mlb-awards-2016-rookie-of-the-year-corey-seager-dodgers/lufcd5w20ksw1bvi89p9qbbpg |title=Dodgers SS Corey Seager wins Sporting News NL Rookie of the Year |first=Ryan |last=Fagan |work=The Sporting News |date=2016-10-24 |accessdate=2016-10-24 |archive-date=2017-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813194222/http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/news/mlb-awards-2016-rookie-of-the-year-corey-seager-dodgers/lufcd5w20ksw1bvi89p9qbbpg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=stephen110916>{{cite web |url=http://www.truebluela.com/2016/11/9/13572300/corey-seager-outstanding-rookie-mlb-players-2016 |title=Corey Seager voted best NL rookie by MLB players |first=Eric |last=Stephen |date=2016-11-09 |accessdate=2016-11-09 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027041354/https://www.truebluela.com/2016/11/9/13572300/corey-seager-outstanding-rookie-mlb-players-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[2016年国家联盟分区赛|國聯分區系列賽]]第1場比賽，席格擊出首打席全壘打，成為道奇隊史季後賽全壘打的最年輕新秀<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.truebluela.com/2016/10/7/13206756/corey-seager-home-run-youngest-dodger-postseason-nlds |title=Corey Seager is youngest Dodger to hit a postseason home run |work=SB Nation |first=Eric |last=Stephen |date=2016-10-07 |accessdate=2016-10-07 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026221213/https://www.truebluela.com/2016/10/7/13206756/corey-seager-home-run-youngest-dodger-postseason-nlds |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

席格獲得球季後的[[美國職棒大聯盟銀棒獎|銀棒獎]]肯定，是道奇隊史第三位新秀獲獎者<ref name=osborne111016>{{cite web |url=https://dodgers.mlblogs.com/corey-seager-silver-slugger-shortstop-40e09ba3c3ff#.jcz540ls1 |title=Corey Seager becomes Dodgers’ first Silver Slugger shortstop |first=Cary|last=Osborne|work=Dodgers Insider |date=2016-11-10 |accessdate=2016-11-10}}</ref>，此外也囊括了所有新人王選票，成為年度國聯新秀<ref name=osborne1114161>{{cite web |url=https://dodgers.mlblogs.com/corey-seager-rookie-year-unanimous-b96285382dd7#.w02b72szh |work=Dodgers.com |first=Cary |last=Osborne |title=It’s unanimous: Corey Seager is NL Rookie of the Year|date=2016-11-14|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref>。

====2017年球季====
6月20日，席格單場擊出3支全壘打，生涯第二次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2017/06/21/corey-seager-hits-3-home-runs-against-mets/103059974/|title=Corey Seager's three-homer game fuels Los Angeles Dodgers' rout of New York Mets|work=USA Today|author=Associated Press|date=2017-06-21|accessdate=2017-11-28|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024113244/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2017/06/21/corey-seager-hits-3-home-runs-against-mets/103059974/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他連續第二年入選[[2017年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|明星賽]]<ref name=2017star>{{cite web|url=https://www.truebluela.com/all-star-game/2017/7/2/15908678/all-star-game-rosters-2017-dodgers-clayton-kershaw-corey-seager-cody-bellinger-kenley-jansen|title=All-Star Game rosters 2017: Dodgers send 4 players to Miami|work=SB Nation|first=Eric|last=Stephen|date=2017-07-02|accessdate=2017-07-02|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123130921/https://www.truebluela.com/all-star-game/2017/7/2/15908678/all-star-game-rosters-2017-dodgers-clayton-kershaw-corey-seager-cody-bellinger-kenley-jansen|dead-url=no}}</ref>，9月時受到手肘傷勢困擾而影響表現<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.truebluela.com/2017/9/19/16332090/corey-seager-elbow-not-100-percent-manage-pain-dodgers|title=Corey Seager’s elbow continues to linger|work=SB Nation|first=Eric|last=Stephen|date=2017-09-19|accessdate=2017-11-28|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031621/https://www.truebluela.com/2017/9/19/16332090/corey-seager-elbow-not-100-percent-manage-pain-dodgers|dead-url=no}}</ref>，季末仍獲得銀棒獎<ref name=2017SS>{{cite web|url=https://www.truebluela.com/2017/11/9/16630460/corey-seager-silver-slugger-award-shortstop-national-league-dodgers|title=Corey Seager wins 2nd Silver Slugger Award at shortstop|first=Eric|last=Stephen|work=SB Nation|date=2017-11-09|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122192016/https://www.truebluela.com/2017/11/9/16630460/corey-seager-silver-slugger-award-shortstop-national-league-dodgers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[2017年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區系列賽]]當中，席格遭遇了背部的運動傷害，使他錯過了[[2017年國家聯盟冠軍賽|國聯冠軍系列賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/back-injury-keeps-corey-seager-off-dodgers-nlcs-roster/2017/10/14/c70e724a-b12d-11e7-a908-a3470754bbb9_story.html|title=Sports Back injury keeps Corey Seager off Dodgers’ NLCS roster|publisher=Washington Post|first=Barry|last=Svluga|date=2017-10-14|accessdate=2017-11-28|archive-date=2019-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117041711/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/back-injury-keeps-corey-seager-off-dodgers-nlcs-roster/2017/10/14/c70e724a-b12d-11e7-a908-a3470754bbb9_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過在之後的[[2017年世界大賽|世界大賽]]中重新被登錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/259373996/dodgers-corey-seager-on-world-series-roster/|title=Seager makes Dodgers' World Series roster|work=mlb.com|first=Ken|last=Gurnick|date=2017-10-24|accessdate=2017-11-28|archive-date=2017-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171106132629/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/259373996/dodgers-corey-seager-on-world-series-roster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在整個世界大賽系列，席格擊出了6支安打（包括2支長打），但道奇在最終戰負於[[休士頓太空人|休士頓太空人]]，與冠軍失之交臂<ref name=br/>。

====2018年球季====
4月30日，席格被發現右肘的尺骨附屬韌帶受損，必須接受[[尺骨附屬韌帶重建術|重建手術]]，整個球季都將無法出賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23369289/corey-seager-los-angeles-dodgers-tommy-john-surgery |title=Dodgers' Corey Seager will have Tommy John surgery and miss rest of season |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |date=2018-04-30 |accessdate=2018-04-30 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109020253/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23369289/corey-seager-los-angeles-dodgers-tommy-john-surgery |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/corey-seager-to-have-tommy-john-surgery/c-274573656 |title=BREAKING: Corey Seager to miss rest of year |website=MLB.com |date=2018-04-30 |accessdate=2018-04-30 |archive-date=2018-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011092438/https://www.mlb.com/news/corey-seager-to-have-tommy-john-surgery/c-274573656 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====2019年球季====
席格在季前與道奇球團達成了一年4,000,000美元的薪資協議，避免了新人仲裁程序<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.salisburypost.com/2019/01/11/corey-seager-reaches-one-year-deal-with-dodgers-martin-headed-back-to-la/|title=Corey Seager reaches one-year deal with Dodgers; Martin headed back to LA - Salisbury Post|date=2019-01-11|work=Salisbury Post|access-date=2019-09-20|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920142432/https://www.salisburypost.com/2019/01/11/corey-seager-reaches-one-year-deal-with-dodgers-martin-headed-back-to-la/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在6月11日的比賽中遭遇了左腿後腱的扭傷，進入傷兵名單<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/corey-seager-to-injured-list-with-hamstring-strain|title=LA likely without Seager till after All-Star break|website=MLB.com|language=en|access-date=2019-09-19|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211170009/https://www.mlb.com/news/corey-seager-to-injured-list-with-hamstring-strain|dead-url=no}}</ref>（受傷前，他在最近的37個打席中繳出.459打擊率）。

7月10日，席格回到先發名單，擔任首棒打者<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/27163309/dodgers-get-even-stronger-seager-returns|title=Dodgers get even stronger as Seager returns|date=2019-07-10|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=2019-09-19|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202105016/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/27163309/dodgers-get-even-stronger-seager-returns|dead-url=no}}</ref>。季末結算，席格在缺席一個月的情形下仍然有44支二壘安打，刷新了個人紀錄<ref name=br/>。

====2020年球季====
季前，席格再次與道奇球團達成薪資協議，其薪資調整為一年7,600,000美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/cody-bellinger-arbitration-record|title=Bellinger sets 1st-year arbitration record|work=MLB.com|first=Ken|last=Gurnick|date=2020-01-10|accessdate=2020-01-11|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101012912/https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/cody-bellinger-arbitration-record|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在縮水賽季中，席格在打擊率、長打率、安打、二壘打、打點等項目皆是道奇打者最佳；對此，他則認為保持健康就是最大的秘訣<ref>{{cite web |last1=Starkand |first1=Daniel |title=Dodgers News: Corey Seager Attributes Successful Season To Health |url=https://dodgerblue.com/dodgers-news-corey-seager-attributes-successful-season-to-health/2020/08/28/ |website=Dodger Blue |accessdate=2020-09-27 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103222427/https://dodgerblue.com/dodgers-news-corey-seager-attributes-successful-season-to-health/2020/08/28/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這點也顯示在他的擊球初速上：[[Statcast|Statcast]]顯示席格的平均擊球初速達到93.2英哩，生涯最佳。

====2021年球季====
該年他和道奇簽下1年1375萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Stephen |first1=Eric |title=Dodgers avoid salary arbitration with Corey Seager, Julio Urías |url=https://www.truebluela.com/2021/1/15/22233031/corey-seager-julio-urias-dodgers-salary-arbitration |access-date=15 January 2021 |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220200731/https://www.truebluela.com/2021/1/15/22233031/corey-seager-julio-urias-dodgers-salary-arbitration |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月15日，他因為被觸身球擊中右手而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/corey-seager-hand-injury|title=Seager fractures hand on HBP, will go on IL|first=Juan|last=Toribio|date=May 15, 2021|accessdate=May 16, 2021|archive-date=2021-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130032254/https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/corey-seager-hand-injury|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月26日，他敲出生涯百轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dodgers.mlblogs.com/dodgers-100th-win-comes-with-middle-infielders-100th-homers-dd9a317e477c|title=Dodgers' 100th win comes with middle infielders' 100th homers|work=Dodgers.com|first=Rowan|last=Kavner|date=September 26, 2021|accessdate=October 11, 2021}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為3成06，並敲出16轟與57分打點。<ref name=br/>季後賽方面，他在分區賽敲出5支安打、國聯冠軍賽敲出4支安打。<ref name=br/>

===德州遊騎兵===
2021年11月29日，遊騎兵以10年3.25億美元的合約簽下席格。

